net.jodah.failsafe

Class FailsafeFuture<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<T>
      • net.jodah.failsafe.FailsafeFuture<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - result type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompletionStage<T>, Future<T>

    public class FailsafeFuture<T>
extends CompletableFuture<T>
    A CompletableFuture implementation that propogates cancellations and calls completion handlers.

    Part of the Failsafe SPI.
